short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Reverts Google Workspace (formerly G Suite) favicons back to pre-2020 icons

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Gets rid of the new identical-looking favicons, reverts to the prior set. Only affects favicons (icons in navbar).

Non-interactive, so the Calendar won't show current date of month, etc.
